{"tid":1252870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持有線電視徹底追究藍絲廢老","createTime":"2019-06-23T09:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T12:57:45.000Z","uid":19552,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"295f96a67d2c6922bcbef82a7be03498aa08c877","tid":1252870,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/23/TuU7Lt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F23%2FTuU7Lt.png&h=45dde108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】有線電視昨發聲明，稱有人在社交媒體擅自使用有線新聞前晚在警察總部外的直播畫面，並自行配上旁白，令人誤以為是該台的報道。有線新聞表示對蓄意誤導公眾的侵權行為，保留一切追究權利。<br />\n在一個有7.7萬名追蹤者的facebook專頁「保普選 反佔中簽左名揮手區！」，昨早仍見一段用上有線新聞直播畫面，配以旁白的片段。負責旁白的是一把男聲，批評包圍警察總部的示威者，亦指現場的人要求警方釋放6．12警民衝突被捕示威者是不合理，形容「那些人是暴徒」。該片段昨晚已下架。<br />\n然而，該專頁仍載有不少now新聞台、有線新聞及無綫新聞的片段，但貼上該專頁名稱的水印，部分遮蓋各新聞台的標記，其中一條印上「612暴徒衝擊立法會實錄」的字幕，畫面是now新聞台在6月12日報道示威者與警員在立法會外衝突的情况，當中有警員擎槍對準示威者的畫面。本報昨以短訊向該專頁查詢，至截稿前未獲回覆。"},{"pid":"c656415eed600ec5c9da88afe01feec9cb37699c","tid":1252870,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ee1a567459440c9ec779e0fcc9df4c4bf9ee8f","tid":1252870,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1487777a2d198ded34016450468cc5f263f31727","tid":1252870,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51320d44024611e4e8cdda33259a2db7bd1d2841","tid":1252870,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d251323925c83944035db245e7f16773d1815aed","tid":1252870,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}